*xf86-input-vmmouse-12.4.2 (14 Sep 2007)

  14 Sep 2007; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  +xf86-input-vmmouse-12.4.2.ebuild:
  Bump for 7.3. Also includes a .modinfo section for easier access of version
  info by VMWare.

  06 Aug 2007; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>; ChangeLog:
  Fix up changelog to stop gentoo.tamperd.net/stable/ warning.

  05 May 2007; Daniel Gryniewicz <dang@gentoo.org>
  xf86-input-vmmouse-12.4.1.ebuild:
  Marked stable on amd64 for bug #175465

  29 Apr 2007; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org>
  xf86-input-vmmouse-12.4.1.ebuild:
  Stable on x86, bug #175465.

*xf86-input-vmmouse-12.4.1 (22 Mar 2007)

