  xf86-input-vmmouse-12.4.0.ebuild:
  AMD64/x86 stable for bug #144549 (X7.1).

  11 Oct 2006; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  xf86-input-vmmouse-12.3.1.0.ebuild, xf86-input-vmmouse-12.3.2.0.ebuild,
